name: MAGA: Fight for Trump
description: Fight For Trump ($TRUMPCOIN) is a meme token inspired by USA President Trump. Being fully community-driven, the token is quickly gaining traction among crypto enthusiasts, particularly Trump supporters. 80% of the the supply is dedicated as an airdrop to active memecoin buyers. 20% all on-chain for market makers, exchange payments, and influencer payments. Fully distributed. The airdrop will be available for claiming up to 5 days after listing. Unclaimed coins can be burned or sent to the public Trump wallet to support the future of America or used for other dev resources/growth.
